From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Sanders <dsanders11@ucsbalum.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 23:29:10 -0700
Subject: chore: add to UBSan ignorelists

Add ignores for false positives:
* `memcpy` with a nullptr dest and zero length is now well-defined per C2y (N3322)
  but glibc still unilaterally marks the dest parameter as `__nonnull`

Add ignores for build failures:
* `AutoPipSettingOverlayView` lacks type info but is pulled into the build via chromium_src
* `Profile` lacks type info but is pulled into the build via chromium_src

Re-enables coverage:
* `RenderWidgetHostViewMac` is a specific subclass that had coverage removed via a broader ignore

Also adds some ignores for UB from upstream code that has been determined to be benign in practice

Change-Id: Ic70cae72965656e31d957ca3cee85772ded70e42

diff --git a/tools/ubsan/ignorelist.txt b/tools/ubsan/ignorelist.txt
index 50c4c61efdf3427285071f3f613957b36ed2e51d..575a0f4f4fad56978344fcbcfb96b2d44fc87773 100644
--- a/tools/ubsan/ignorelist.txt
+++ b/tools/ubsan/ignorelist.txt
@@ -42,3 +42,17 @@ fun:*find_best_partition_order_*
 # https://crbug.com/451633108
 [builtin]
 fun:*_dispatch_once*
+
+#############################################################################
+# Electron-specific
+#
+
+# memcpy with a NULL dest and 0 write length is well-defined per C2y (N3322),
+# but glibc still marks memcpy's dest parameter as __nonnull
+[nonnull-attribute]
+fun:*StringBytes*Write*
+fun:*Http2Session*OnStreamRead*
+
+# This is a benign alignment UB
+[alignment]
+fun:*v8*internal*Script*Iterator*Next*
diff --git a/tools/ubsan/vptr_ignorelist.txt b/tools/ubsan/vptr_ignorelist.txt
index 20c4222c780951af064a10f64264db958b1b8009..993bd090a1d720162da050463dddd76095328c89 100644
--- a/tools/ubsan/vptr_ignorelist.txt
+++ b/tools/ubsan/vptr_ignorelist.txt
@@ -126,3 +126,15 @@ type:*StartPageService*
 # Remove once function attribute level ignorelisting is implemented.
 # See crbug.com/476063.
 fun:*forbidGCDuringConstruction*
+
+#############################################################################
+# Electron-specific ignores
+#
+type:*AutoPipSettingOverlayView*
+type:*Profile*
+
+# Re-enable checks for RenderWidgetHostViewMac
+type:*RenderWidgetHostViewMac*=sanitize
+
+# This has a static_cast that is UB but is benign
+fun:*AudioManagerMac*ReleaseInputStream*
